001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.service;
002
003import edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model.Game;
004import edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model.Guess;
005import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Single;
006import retrofit2.http.Body;
007import retrofit2.http.GET;
008import retrofit2.http.Header;
009import retrofit2.http.POST;
010import retrofit2.http.Path;
011
012/**
013 * Gets games, game ID's, and the list of guesses from a specific game
014 */
015public interface TeamleServiceProxy {
016
017  @POST("games")
018  Single<Game> startGame(@Body Game game, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
019
020  @GET("games/{id}")
021  Single<Game> getGame(@Path("id") String id, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
022
023  @POST("games/{id}/guesses")
024  Single<Guess> submitGuess(@Body Guess guess, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
025
026}
